title: Jimmy Fallon jokes on Drew Brees, Saints teammates on 'The Tonight Show'
text:
Comedian and late-night talk show host Jimmy Fallon panned a handful of New Orleans Saints players, including quarterback Drew Brees, during his weekly Thursday NFL superlatives segment.
Check them out:
Quarterback Drew Brees
 Fullback Austin Johnson
 Cornerback Delvin Breaux
 Linebacker Stephone Anthony Center Max Unger
 Linebacker Hau'oli Kikaha Jeff Duncan, NOLA.com | The Times-Picayune
